description:
This is a keystroke launcher for Windows and macOS.


New features:
- Added new Password Generator extension (Thanks @MarcoSennHaag)
Improvements:
- File Search extension: added option to navigate back with Esc key (Thanks @MarcoSennHaag)
- VSCode extension: added option to search file system (Thanks @IrishBruse)
- UUID Generator extension: Added option to validate invalid UUIDs (Thanks @MarcoSennHaag)
Bug fixes:
- Fixed bug that caused the "No search results found" message not to appear
